channel.title: Arksun
channel.description:
hey rate this tune
http://onlyonerule.pwnds.info/Arksun%20-%20Arisen.mp3 (its freeware)
i rate it 10/10, nice and simple, lively and effective trance tune, perfect build up and ending, very good variation. in my mind the best trance tune yet. but yet its free then well known djs like Armin Van Buren take it, remix it and set it on a cd (A State Of Trance 2006) and make millions from it, although i cant say iu hate Armin Van Bruen :P
